{"tid":1469450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個人認為千千萬萬唔可以呼籲民陣遊行之後入機場！！","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:04:25.000Z","uid":22360,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc094cd73870cc943f7a91fd8e32dd4494ee77c","tid":1469450,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:53:38.000Z","msg":"今次嘅抗爭之所以可以堅持到呢個地步係因為我哋有一套模式<br />\n<br />\n1. 不合作運動<br />\n2. 衝擊<br />\n3. 經濟戰<br />\n4. 和平遊行<br />\n<br />\n文珍搞嘅遊行絕對要係極之和平，換句話來講，係要行完之後極速散水！我知道大家可能會覺得咁樣做係浪費左一日嘅人力，做唔到實事非常可惜，但係我哋唔能夠忽略民陣嘅遊行其實係我哋檢測民意，凝聚民意嘅唯一一個行動方式，絕對絕對不能夠同其他嘅行動混合埋一齊，咁樣只會令我哋失去左其中一種行動模式！"},{"pid":"fbe80bbef72b54d69a7efbae6fe2c4b70ff60cc6","tid":1469450,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:54:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabffd34d988b5b5f771d752db8617c8154f35a2","tid":1469450,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:02:44.000Z","msg":"入機場坐就好<br />\n唔好示威"},{"pid":"5a59404870578ddb806706b931612fb0d21b18de","tid":1469450,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:04:25.000Z","msg":"係要遊行前設升級死線<br />\n遊行完唔回應既話就  24小時後升級"}]}